title: NFL Draft: Top 10 Quarterback Prospects with Danny Kanell (Football 4/7)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Danny Kanell to kick off offensive prospect rankings week on the Pick Six podcast. Danny ranks his Top 10 quarterbacks in the 2020 NFL Draft. How does Tua Tagovailoa's health affect his ranking? Who could be the sleeper from this class? And most importantly, who is this year's Danny Kanell? Listen in as we breakdown the future of the most crucial position in football.

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
